@lilars: Finaly... and I wrote comments to myself whole day.
Not that no one has downloaded my "shit which sucks", quite contrary, a few - hundreds till now, but you have been first who have "spoken" so far.
@20/40 I'm glad I could brighten your day a little with something so small as a thank you.

Hi 20-40,
Thanks for the encode/upload.

I LOVE quark!!!

I would've commented to say thanks before now but spent weekend painting. No fun at all. I still haven't seen most of last weeks shows.

BTW, I am getting into Craig Ferguson - thanks for recommendation (it was to someone else) but it sounded good and I'm beginning to become a fan! Have to see if the show keeps up it's high production values, HA!

Thanks for LOTS also.

Cheers
Jon

Hi Lilars, whats even worse is the weather is actually OK, which means it is not raining. Only 2nd weekend so far this year. Did not want to be inhaling paint fumes.

Cheers
Jon
This is the first [quark ] i have downloaded. it is so great ,i cant believe how great it is. thank you so much . with it being so small i can seed longer with out taking up space .thanks twentyforty
